  <h2>Key Features</h2>

  <ul>
    <li><strong>Zero Config</strong> — Auto-detects React, Vue, Svelte, Angular, Tailwind</li>
    <li><strong>Health Scoring</strong> — 0-100 score showing your design system health</li>
    <li><strong>Token Comparison</strong> — Compare against Figma/Tokens Studio exports</li>
    <li><strong>CI Integration</strong> — Catch drift in pull requests before merge</li>
    <li><strong>Typo Detection</strong> — Finds values that are "close" to tokens (likely mistakes)</li>
  </ul>

